    "body": "## Scope\n\nFix the final Safari-confirmed false-negative in the Boomer Step 4.4B current-contract adapter.\n\nExact base: `2858b810a2c14ced38923497b60069b4dc48b95c`.\n\nChanged paths exactly four:\n- `AsyncScene/Web/dev/boomer-step4-4b-current-contract-adapter.js`\n- `docs/dev/boomer-step4-4b-current-contract-adapter.js`\n- `AsyncScene/Web/index.html`\n- `docs/index.html`\n\nAdapter mirrors are byte-identical at Git blob `76be43cbaff7edf9288cae6b44bfea95791efbc9`.\nIndex mirrors are byte-identical at Git blob `4584957197a161451b5ba521d11e0ad6aa614e85`.\nEach index changes only the adapter cache-bust from `20260722a` to `20260722b`.\n\n## Safari evidence\n\nPost-PR254 Safari result:\n- adapter loaded: true\n- current and legacyRaw registrations: function\n- recentRuntimeErrors: []\n- thrown: null\n- static audit: ok:true\n- current profile architecture: ok:true\n- legacy base health: ok:true\n- all seven restoration booleans: true\n- all six adversarial restoration fixtures: true\n- only remaining failure: `emoji_contracts`\n\nExact failed evidence:\n- `dataHits: [💰, ⚡]`\n- DOM: `points:💰`, `rep:⭐`, `influence:⚡`\n- `domOk:true`\n\nThe v1 adapter incorrectly required all three emoji to be present in the scanned data set *and* required exact DOM coverage. Current accepted 4.4A authority already separately validates the live static surfaces, while runtime evidence shows the missing `⭐` is present in the canonical DOM representation.\n\n## Repair\n\nAdapter v2:\n- scans `Data.CAP_MESSAGES` both as active-profile getter output and as possible profile map;\n- records `dataHits`, `domHits`, and `combinedHits`;\n- requires combined current runtime coverage of `💰/⭐/⚡` plus exact DOM mapping `points=💰`, `rep=⭐`, `influence=⚡`;\n- preserves the static 4.4A authority requirement, profile architecture checks, meaningful legacy base health checks, all raw non-superseded checks, all restoration checks, all six adversarial fixtures, and loaded-runtime-asset validation fail-closed.\n\nAdapter identity advances to:\n- `build_2026_07_22_step4_4b_boomer_current_contract_adapter_v2`\n- `boomer_step4_4b_current_contract_adapter_v20260722_002`\n\nNo product copy, gameplay, economy, battle, NPC, state, persistence, or existing `dev-checks.js` source changes.",
